{"tid":1741560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九站過關押大陸嚴刑拷問 國安逼前領館職員認英國策劃反送中","createTime":"2019-11-20T11:36:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T12:13:19.000Z","uid":113024,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"30ef091a9455b440a5cfc1e4f889d2079a05cdc9","tid":1741560,"uid":113024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:36:12.000Z","msg":"任職香港英國領事館職員的港人鄭文傑（Simon Cheng），8月8日經羅湖口岸入境深圳，同日夜晚通知女友搭高鐵回港及在西九高鐵站「過境」時失聯，13天後深圳公安方證實鄭遭行政拘留，至8月24日獲釋。已離職的鄭文傑，近日接受BBC（英國廣播公司）、《The Telegraph》（每日電訊報）及《華爾街日報》等多間外媒訪問。鄭首度公開披露被捕後情況，扣查期間他曾遭國安施刑拷問，迫令他指控英國政府是策劃香港反送中示威的黑手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191120/60289223?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191120%2F60289223%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=266b72a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191120%2F60289223%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=899f7227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191120/60289223?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"4b58861477c0be155f5e1bab67c3798b3e17686f","tid":1741560,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d722fa66531fc3d56e9a723b5a818ab61a9ed3","tid":1741560,"uid":113024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"p